ElementDescription: MDD Current Symptom Count - strict: Dimension 1 (symptoms 1,2,5 - always assessed), only the threshold item is counted as 1
MDD Current Symptom Count - strict: Dimension 2 (all symptoms, if past OR current not skipped out), only the threshold item is counted as 1
MDD Symptom Since Last Visit Count - strict: Dimension 1 (symptoms 1,2,5 - always assessed), only the threshold item is counted as 1
MDD Symptom Since Last Visit Count - strict: Dimension 2 (all symptoms, if past not skipped out), only the threshold item is counted as 1
MDD Current Symptom Count - relaxed: Dimension 1 (symptoms 1,2,5 - always assessed), threshold item is counted as 1 or subthreshold as 0.5
MDD Current Symptom Count - relaxed: Dimension 2 (all symptoms, if past OR current not skipped out), threshold item is counted as 1 or subthreshold as 0.5
MDD Symptom Since Last Visit Count - relaxed: Dimension 1 (symptoms 1,2,5 - always assessed), threshold item is counted as 1 or subthreshold as 0.5
MDD Symptom Since Last Visit Count - relaxed: Dimension 2 (all symptoms, if past not skipped out), threshold item is counted as 1 or subthreshold as 0.5
